asset.title: 2012, 2013 & 2014 Honda Civic 1.8L Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to install the K&N 69-1020TS Cold Air Intake System in your Honda Civic 1.8L. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-1020TS

This intake system created an estimated gain of 3.2 horsepower at 5,424 RPM and 2.1 lb. ft. of torque at 4,836 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

Visit the product page for an up to date vehicle application list.

http://www.KNfilters.com

K&N 69-1020TS fits:
2014 HONDA CIVIC 1.8L 
2013 HONDA CIVIC 1.8L 
2012 HONDA CIVIC 1.8L
